{{Chembox | ImageFile = Pseudoisocyanine.svg | ImageSize = | ImageAlt = The chemical structure of decynium-22 | IUPACName = 1-Ethyl-2-[(1-ethyl-2(1''H'')-quinolinylidene)methyl]quinolinium iodide | OtherNames = {{unbulleted list|Decynium-22|Pseudocyanine iodide|Pseudoisocyanine iodide}} |Section1={{Chembox Identifiers | CASNo = 977-96-8 | PubChem = 5484462 | SMILES = CCN1C(=CC2=[N+](C3=CC=CC=C3C=C2)CC)C=CC4=CC=CC=C41.[I-] | ChemSpiderID = 4588533 | InChI = 1/C23H23N2.HI/c1-3-24-20(15-13-18-9-5-7-11-22(18)24)17-21-16-14-19-10-6-8-12-23(19)25(21)4-2;/h5-17H,3-4H2,1-2H3;1H/q+1;/p-1 | InChIKey = GMYRVMSXMHEDTL-REWHXWOFAU | StdInChI = 1S/C23H23N2.HI/c1-3-24-20(15-13-18-9-5-7-11-22(18)24)17-21-16-14-19-10-6-8-12-23(19)25(21)4-2;/h5-17H,3-4H2,1-2H3;1H/q+1;/p-1 | StdInChIKey = GMYRVMSXMHEDTL-UHFFFAOYSA-M
