'''Manny Calonzo''' is an environmental advocate.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.goldmanprize.org/blog/2018-goldman-prize-winners/|title=Announcing the 2018 Goldman Prize winners|date=2018-04-23|work=Goldman Environmental Foundation|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref> Aided by the Ecological Waste Coalition of the Philippines (EcoWaste) – an organization he founded<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.greengrants.org/2018/04/24/2018goldman/|title=Grassroots Environmental Heroes: The 2018 Goldman Environmental Prize Winners|last=|first=|date=|website=www.greengrants.org|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2018-08-19}}</ref> – he was responsible for the [[Government of the Philippines|Philippine government]]’s law to nationally ban [[lead paint]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.philstar.com/business/science-and-environment/2018/04/26/1809382/pinoy-6-others-win-environmental-prize|title=Pinoy, 6 others win environmental prize {{!}} Philstar.com|website=philstar.com|access-date=2018-08-19}}</ref> (culminating in 85% lead-certified paint there since 2017)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180422005092/en/Goldman-Environmental-Prize-Honors-Environmental-Heroes|title=Goldman Environmental Prize Honors Seven Environmental Heroes|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en}}</ref> and the creation of a third-party certification program<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.mb.com.ph/2018/04/23/filipino-among-seven-2018-goldman-environmental-prize-awardees/|title=Filipino among seven 2018 Goldman Environmental Prize awardees|work=Manila Bulletin News|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref> for paint manufacturers.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.goldmanprize.org/recipient/manny-calonzo/|title=Manny Calonzo - Goldman Environmental Foundation|work=Goldman Environmental Foundation|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref> His anti-toxic campaign extended to other substances in [[footwear]] items which potentially decreased [[fertility]] in men and harmed [[Fetus|fetuses]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/985125/pinoy-campaigner-vs-lead-paint-6-others-win-environmental-prize|title=Pinoy campaigner vs lead paint, 6 others win environmental prize|last=Inquirer|first=Philippine Daily|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en}}</ref> In 2018 he was one of seven<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.mongabay.com/2018/04/meet-the-winners-of-the-2018-goldman-environmental-prize/|title=Meet the winners of the 2018 Goldman Environmental Prize|date=2018-04-23|work=Mongabay Environmental News|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref> international [[Goldman Environmental Prize]] winners<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/environment/gallery/2018/apr/23/2018-goldman-environmental-prize-the-winners-in-pictures|title=2018 Goldman environmental prize - the winners in pictures|date=2018-04-23|work=The Guardian|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077}}</ref> – a decade after he began his national campaign<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.abs-cbn.com/focus/04/23/18/filipino-bags-international-award-for-campaign-vs-lead-paint|title=Filipino bags international award for campaign vs lead paint|last=News|first=ABS-CBN|work=ABS-CBN News|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.goodnewspilipinas.com/manny-calonzo-wins-intl-environment-award-for-campaign-vs-lead-paint/|title=Manny Calonzo wins Int’l Environment Award for campaign vs lead paint|date=2018-04-25|work=Good News Pilipinas|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref> – which resulted in the protection of millions of Filipino children.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2018/04/youll-probably-never-save-as-many-lives-as-this-guy-who-got-the-philippines-to-stop-using-lead-paint/|title=You'll probably never save as many lives as this guy who got the Philippines to stop using lead paint|work=Mother Jones|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref> Calonzo is a [[consultant]] on the Global Lead Paint Elimination Campaign at the International Persistent Organic Pollutants Elimination Network.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://financialtribune.com/articles/environment/85162/goldman-environmental-prize-winners-announced|title=Goldman Environmental Prize Winners Announced|date=2018-04-23|work=Financial Tribune|access-date=2018-08-19|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ipen.org/news/goldman-environmental-prize-winner-manny-calonzo-painting-brighter-future-our-children-lead|title=Goldman Environmental Prize Winner Manny Calonzo: Painting a Brighter Future for Our Children with Lead Safe Paint  {{!}} IPEN|website=ipen.org|language=en|access-date=2018-08-19}}</ref>

